<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Go в примери: Подреждане чрез функции</title>
    <link rel=stylesheet href="site.css">
  </head>
  <script>
      window.onkeydown = (e) => {
          if (e.ctrlKey || e.altKey || e.shiftKey || e.metaKey) {
              return;
          }
          
          if (e.key == "ArrowLeft") {
              window.location.href = 'sorting';
          }
          
          
          if (e.key == "ArrowRight") {
              window.location.href = 'panic';
          }
          
      }
  </script>
  <body>
    <div class="example" id="sorting-by-functions">
      <h2><a href="./">Go в примери</a>: Подреждане чрез функции</h2>
      
      <table>
        
        <tr>
          <td class="docs">
            <p>Понякога може да искаме да подредим някакъв набор от
неща по някакъв друг признак, а не по естесвения им
ред. Например нека си представим, че искаме да подредим
набор от низове според тяхната дължина вместо по
азбучен ред. Ето един пример с определено от
потребителя на Го подреждане.</p>

          </td>
          <td class="code empty leading">
            
          
          </td>
        </tr>
        
        <tr>
          <td class="docs">
            
          </td>
          <td class="code leading">
            <a href="https://go.dev/play/p/uBuFQe2VtV_3"><img title="Run code" src="play.png" class="run" /></a><img title="Copy code" src="clipboard.png" class="copy" />
          <pre class="chroma"><code><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="kn">package</span> <span class="nx">main</span></span></span></code></pre>
          </td>
        </tr>
        
        <tr>
          <td class="docs">
            
          </td>
          <td class="code leading">
            
          <pre class="chroma"><code><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="kn">import</span> <span class="p">(</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="s">&#34;cmp&#34;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="s">&#34;fmt&#34;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="s">&#34;slices&#34;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">)</span></span></span></code></pre>
          </td>
        </tr>
        
        <tr>
          <td class="docs">
            
          </td>
          <td class="code leading">
            
          <pre class="chroma"><code><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="kd">func</span> <span class="nf">main</span><span class="p">()</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="nx">плодове</span> <span class="o">:=</span> <span class="p">[]</span><span class="kt">string</span><span class="p">{</span><span class="s">&#34;праскова&#34;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">&#34;банан&#34;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">&#34;киви&#34;</span><span class="p">}</span></span></span></code></pre>
          </td>
        </tr>
        
        <tr>
          <td class="docs">
            <p>Осъществяваме функция, която сравнява дължините на
два низа. <code>cmp.Compare</code> ни върши работа в тоя
случай.</p>

          </td>
          <td class="code leading">
            
          <pre class="chroma"><code><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="nx">lenCmp</span> <span class="o">:=</span> <span class="kd">func</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">a</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nx">b</span> <span class="kt">string</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="kt">int</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="k">return</span> <span class="nx">cmp</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nf">Compare</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">a</span><span class="p">),</span> <span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">b</span><span class="p">))</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="p">}</span></span></span></code></pre>
          </td>
        </tr>
        
        <tr>
          <td class="docs">
            <p>Сега можем да извикаме <code>slices.SortFunc</code> с нашата
потребителска функция за сравнение, за да подредим
отрязъка <code>плодове</code> по дължина на името.</p>

          </td>
          <td class="code leading">
            
          <pre class="chroma"><code><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="nx">slices</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nf">SortFunc</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">плодове</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nx">lenCmp</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="nx">fmt</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nf">Println</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">плодове</span><span class="p">)</span></span></span></code></pre>
          </td>
        </tr>
        
        <tr>
          <td class="docs">
            <p>Можем да ползваме същия подход и за невградени
в езика видове данни.</p>

          </td>
          <td class="code leading">
            
          <pre class="chroma"><code><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="kd">type</span> <span class="nx">Личност</span> <span class="kd">struct</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="nx">име</span>     <span class="kt">string</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="nx">възраст</span> <span class="kt">int</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="p">}</span></span></span></code></pre>
          </td>
        </tr>
        
        <tr>
          <td class="docs">
            
          </td>
          <td class="code leading">
            
          <pre class="chroma"><code><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="nx">народ</span> <span class="o">:=</span> <span class="p">[]</span><span class="nx">Личност</span><span class="p">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="nx">Личност</span><span class="p">{</span><span class="nx">име</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s">&#34;Пешо&#34;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nx">възраст</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="mi">37</span><span class="p">},</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="nx">Личност</span><span class="p">{</span><span class="nx">име</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s">&#34;Иван&#34;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nx">възраст</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="mi">25</span><span class="p">},</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="nx">Личност</span><span class="p">{</span><span class="nx">име</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s">&#34;Краси&#34;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nx">възраст</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="mi">72</span><span class="p">},</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="p">}</span></span></span></code></pre>
          </td>
        </tr>
        
        <tr>
          <td class="docs">
            <p>Подреждаме <code>народ</code> по възраст с помощта на
<code>slices.SortFunc</code>.</p>

<p>Забележка: ако структурата <code>Личност</code> е голяма може
би ще предпочетете отрязъка да съдържа <code>*Личност</code>и
и да преправите подреждащата си функция. Ако се
колебаете, прочетете
<a href="testing-and-benchmarking">benchmark</a>!</p>

          </td>
          <td class="code">
            
          <pre class="chroma"><code><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="nx">slices</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nf">SortFunc</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">народ</span><span class="p">,</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="kd">func</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">a</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nx">b</span> <span class="nx">Личност</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="kt">int</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">            <span class="k">return</span> <span class="nx">cmp</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nf">Compare</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">a</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">възраст</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nx">b</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">възраст</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="p">})</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="nx">fmt</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nf">Println</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">народ</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">}</span></span></span></code></pre>
          </td>
        </tr>
        
      </table>
      
      <table>
        
        <tr>
          <td class="docs">
            
          </td>
          <td class="code">
            
          <pre class="chroma"><code><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="gp">$</span> go run sorting-by-functions.go 
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="go">[киви банан праскова]
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="go">[{Иван 25} {Пешо 37} {Краси 72}]</span></span></span></code></pre>
          </td>
        </tr>
        
      </table>
      
      
